<div class="headerbox">
      <h1>Direct Mail/Online Ads</h1>
</div>
More than one million pieces of direct mail and more than four million impressions of electronic direct mail to 200,000 unique readers keep International CES attendees up-to-date. Reach CES&#39; online community through these opportunities.<br />

<a name="#Top">&nbsp;</a>
<div style="color: #233c82; font-size: 1.4em; padding-bottom: 10px;"><strong>&gt;&nbsp;On this page:</strong></div>
<div class="onThisPageItem">
    <a href="#55">Ads on CESweb.org</a>
</div><div class="onThisPageItem">
    <a href="#56">Attendee Newsletter Sponsorships</a>
</div><div class="onThisPageItem">
    <a href="#57">Attendee Postal Mailing List</a>
</div><div class="onThisPageItem">
    <a href="#62">Dedicated Email Blasts</a>
</div>
<div style="clear: both; padding-bottom: 20px;"></div><div style="margin-top: 50px; clear: both;" ></div>

<hr />
<a name="55">&nbsp;</a>
<div class="sponsorshipTitle">Ads on CESweb.org:&nbsp;<span class="lt_blue">$7,500</span></div>
<br />
The official online source for all International CES information, CESweb.org attracts thousands of qualified, consumer technology professionals each day. Online ads, especially when placed on well-trafficked, highly visible pages, can be one of the most effective and affordable marketing vehicles today. Receive online space during the show&#39;s busiest online time &mdash; September through January.<br />
<br />
Ads can appear on pages such as:<br />
<br />
Main conference program page: <a href="http://www.cesweb.org/Conference-Program.aspx">CESweb.org/Conference-Program.aspx</a><br />
Main events page: <a href="http://www.cesweb.org/Events.aspx">CESweb.org/Events.aspx</a><br />
Main show floor page: <a href="http://www.cesweb.org/Show-Floor.aspx">CESweb.org/Show-Floor.aspx</a><br />
Main hotel/travel page: <a href="http://www.cesweb.org/Hotel-Travel.aspx">CESweb.org/Hotel-Travel.aspx</a><br />
Main press page: <a href="http://www.cesweb.org/For-The-Press.aspx">CESweb.org/For-The-Press.aspx</a><br />
Main FAQs page: <a href="http://www.cesweb.org/FAQ.aspx">CESweb.org/FAQ.aspx</a><br />
<br />
Banner ads may run September 1, 2012-February 1, 2013.<br />
<br />
Technical Specifications of Banner Ads: We accept static GIF and JPG images.<br />
<br />




<p></p>
<p></p>
<strong>contact</strong><br />CES Promotional Opportunities Manager&nbsp;<br />Phone:&nbsp;703-907-4324<br />Email:&nbsp;<a href="mailto:byb@CE.org">byb@CE.org</a>
