<a name="56">&nbsp;</a>
<div class="sponsorshipTitle">Attendee Newsletter Sponsorships:&nbsp;<span class="lt_blue">$5,000+</span></div>
<br />
<em><img alt="" src="/cesweb/media/CESWeb/Promo%20Opps/Direct%20Mail%20Online%20Ads/CES_DirectMailOnlineAds_UTTMSponsorSample.gif" style="width: 150px; height: 264px; float: right; " />CES Up to</em><em> the </em><em>Minute </em>is the regularly scheduled attendee newsletter that deploys to our attendees and prospects. Take advantage of this promotional opportunity by adding your message to our Partner Spotlight - the exhibitor advertisement section of the newsletter. Exhibitor advertisements are limited to 50 words, logo and URL. Through each newsletter you have the opportunity of reaching more than 200,000 readers, including 2013 pre-registered attendees, 2012 attendees, prospects, international attendees, VIP buyers and more.<br />
&nbsp;<br />
Don&rsquo;t miss out on this opportunity to include a logo, URL and 50 words about your company and product in our regularly scheduled attendee newsletter, <em>CES Up to The Minute</em>. Call now for details.&nbsp;<br />
<br />
<a href="/getattachment/b51618a4-e6d4-4aae-9598-7d1d91a306a3/CES_DirectMailOnlineAds_UTTMSponsorSample.gif.aspx" target="_blank">Download the flyer&nbsp;for more information and drop date options</a>.<br />
<br />
<br />




<p></p>
<p><strong>Sponsorship Benefit:</strong><br /><ul><li>CES Exhibitors: $5,000 for one newsletter sponsorship; $8,000 for two. 

Exclusive Opportunities Available</li>
</ul></p>
<strong>contact</strong><br />CES Promotional Opportunities Manager&nbsp;<br />Phone:&nbsp;703-907-4324<br />Email:&nbsp;<a href="mailto:byb@CE.org">byb@CE.org</a>
