    <hr />
<a name="57">&nbsp;</a>
<div class="sponsorshipTitle">Attendee Postal Mailing List:&nbsp;<span class="lt_blue">$1,000+</span></div>
<br />
The International CES attendee mailing lists, available only to CES exhibitors, help you reach last year&#39;s show attendees and those who have pre-registered to attend the International CES. We&#39;ll help you target specific demographics of attendees you want to see at your booth. Contact them via direct mail, before the show doors open, and reinforce your messaging to our verified lists.&nbsp;<br />
<br />
<strong>Requirements:</strong><br />
<ul>
	<li>
		Must be an International CES exhibitor</li>
	<li>
		Must be a CES-approved postal direct mail piece</li>
	<li>
		Only mailing addresses are available (no e-mail addresses)&nbsp;</li>
	<li>
		All mailings must go through a third-party mail house&nbsp;</li>
</ul>




<p></p>
<p></p>
<strong>contact</strong><br />Melissa Hopson, Experient&nbsp;<br />Phone:&nbsp;866-221-7921; 240-439-2307<br />Email:&nbsp;<a href="mailto:Melissa.hopson@experient-inc.com">Melissa.hopson@experient-inc.com</a>
<div style="padding: 25px 0 25px 0;"><a class="back_to_top" href="#">[back to top]</a></div>
    <hr />
<a name="62">&nbsp;</a>
<div class="sponsorshipTitle">Dedicated Email Blasts:&nbsp;<span class="lt_blue">$15,000+</span></div>
<br />
Send a dedicated email blast, fully-branded to your company to CES attendees through our dedicated HTML email blasts. These blasts are created entirely by you and will be sent out directly by CES on your behalf. Through each e-mail blast, you will have the opportunity to reach more than 200,000 readers including 2013 CES pre-registrants, 2012 verified attendees, prospects, international attendees, VIP buyers and more.<br />
<br />
<strong>Restrictions</strong>:<br />
<ul>
	<li>
		Must be an&nbsp;International CES exhibitor</li>
	<li>
		Promotion must pertain to exhibitor&rsquo;s presence at the International CES, and include CES logo, show dates and website. All images and files must be housed on exhibitor&rsquo;s own server. CEA will not be able to house your images for you.</li>
</ul>
